{"title":"儿童的歌声","authors":["舒特乌·埃列娜　陈陆平"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":2,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿童的歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔罗马尼亚〕舒特乌·埃列娜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界的儿童在歌唱和平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子们应该得到和平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们不愿看到战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愿让鲜花蒙受寒冻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们大人要爱大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要爱这大地上永恒的和平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这甜蜜的、晴朗的和平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么像你们孩子们的眼睛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们也曾是群儿童，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但你们中有多少人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还记得那童年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来吧，来吧，和我们一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着宇宙，向着未来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱这永恒的和平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（陈陆平　译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}